Package hrps.entity

Class CheckedInReservation

  • java.lang.Object
    • hrps.entity.Reservation
      • hrps.entity.CheckedInReservation
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable
    public class CheckedInReservation
extends Reservation
implements java.io.Serializable
    This subclass represents checked-in reservations which are created when guest of a confirmed reservation checked-in. This type of reservation has the ability to order room services.
    Author:
    An Ruyi, Peng Wenxuan
